#Welcome Function: This function displays all the tabs the user can use. (Navigation, New Places, and Visits)

<div show-header="true" show-footer="true" show-top-tabs="true" show-tabs="true"
ng-controller="Welcome" ng-cloak ng-init="init()" class="aio-empty-screen padding overflow-scroll">
    <label class="item item-input">
        <textarea placeholder="Where to visit next"></textarea>
    </label>
    <div class="button-bar">
        <button class="button button-block" navigate-to="gps">
            Navigation
        </button>
        <button class="button button-block" navigate-to="visits">
            Visits
        </button>
        <button class="button button-block">
            New Places
        </button>
    </div>
</div>

#Visit Function: This tab will display all the reviews and places the user has visited

